{"tid":945191,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[秒經] 一人一首人大左先明既歌","createTime":"2018-12-17T16:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T04:14:19.000Z","uid":49813,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d081514bf858cec148019ac76eee44f875b5f0e2","tid":945191,"uid":49813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"最近聽到劉華首笨小孩先開始明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n哦～　<br />\n轉眼間那麼快　這一個笨小孩　又到了捌零年代<br />\n三十歲到頭來　不算好也不壞　經過了玖零年代<br />\n最無奈 他自己　總是會慢人家一拍　沒有錢在那口袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d965904beb502efa94eb4861b0641393403705f0","tid":945191,"uid":77235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:25:28.000Z","msg":"唔好咁悲觀<br />\n哎喲　往著胸口拍一拍呀　勇敢站起來　不用心情太壞<br />\n哎喲　向著天空拜一拜呀　別想不開　老天自有安排"},{"pid":"e5d684a58a6628c3615c81bc4a3c55094195c25b","tid":945191,"uid":356,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:26:15.000Z","msg":"最心痛是 愛得太避"},{"pid":"5fc529808ebf759cfe43f50d38616e38f5d0fc09","tid":945191,"uid":356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最心痛是 愛得太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"353b9535ce5d2ed48ea80097b54f1db8e37ccee7","tid":945191,"uid":50632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:30:23.000Z","msg":"時日太快 無知的小孩 一晚長大<br />\n有些愛 身邊擦過 無奈眼光未放大<br />\n才明白 能活於一分一秒 當下仍愉快<br />\n咬緊拳頭 不怕捱<br />\n青蔥歲月會跑得很快"},{"pid":"056a9e188d3a2f6c26c1272bc7b0c1d37e9f6c82","tid":945191,"uid":6964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"皇后大道東for sure"},{"pid":"12e98e3c94bfe79a3964a1c16e7e87d041f4baa4","tid":945191,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"時光機"},{"pid":"2a8317449163f4358a99a4e32d06ea639ce899dd","tid":945191,"uid":36316,"like":2,"dislike":